746
00:45:36,260 --> 00:45:41,024
<i>♫ The heart gradually silences ♫</i>

747
00:45:42,404 --> 00:45:48,992
<i>♫ Your traces remain in my mind ♫</i>

748
00:45:48,992 --> 00:45:54,464
<i>♫ I can't delete them ♫</i>

749
00:45:55,140 --> 00:46:01,024
<i>♫ Time drips away bit by bit ♫</i>

