00:46:01,024 --> 00:46:07,968
<i>♫ Memories are scattered everywhere ♫</i>

751
00:46:07,968 --> 00:46:16,480
<i>♫ The passing trees cast shadows like you ♫</i>

752
00:46:17,284 --> 00:46:21,120
<i>♫ Fading away ♫</i>

753
00:46:22,308 --> 00:46:28,832
<i>♫ Change the details bit by bit ♫</i>

754
00:46:28,832 --> 00:46:35,616
<i>♫ Decide our fate
